    autogen                     Regenerate autoconf and automake scripts
    autoremove                  Clean all objects found in .gitignore

Build Configuration
    configure.ac                autoconf —
                                    Library and compatibility checker for project setup
    Makefile.am                 automake —
                                    Makefile generator config for autoconf

Tested Build Environments
